snippet.title: Terrible Teeth Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as Cornelius, a heroic kernel of corn trying to save his buddies from certain doom! You have been trapped inside the mouth of a radioactive monster with no escape! Run, jump, dodge and duck to avoid peril. Be warned: The mouth isn't the only danger! Watch out for tooth fairies and other obstacles along the way.

Android:  https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.vilemedia.terribleteeth
iOS:  https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/terrible-teeth/id776445995?ls=1&mt=8


Please help spread the word about this highly addictive new platform game!

#cornstuckinmyteeth
